<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.5">
<l>ēṟṟi ṉaiyima yattuḷem mīcaṉai yimmai yaimaṟu maikkuma runtiṉai</l>
<l>āṟṟa laiyaṇṭat tappuṟat tuyttiṭu maiya ṉaikkaiyi lāḻiyoṉ ṟēntiya</l>
<l>kūṟṟi ṉaikuru māmaṇik kuṉṟiṉai niṉṟa vūrniṉṟa nittilat tottiṉai</l>
<l>kāṟṟi ṉaippuṉa laicceṉṟu nāṭik kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone searching, I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai [the one who is]</l>
<l>A bull, our Īśa in the Himālayas, this life, a potion for the next life, strength,</l>
<l>The master who fully guides [us] beyond heaven,</l>
<l rend="indent">death who bears a discus in hand,</l>
<l>A huge, dark jeweled mountain, the cluster of pearls</l>
<l rend="indent">which remains in Niṉṟavūr, wind, and water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
